Mix together the chopped radicchio and basil. Slice the rolls lengthwise. Begin sandwich build with basil-radicchio mixture, then pepperonchinis, distributing evenly among the four sandwiches. Layer Margherita(R) Salami, Pepperoni and Capicola on each sandwich. Combine mayonnaise and crushed roasted garlic in a bowl until thoroughly mixed. Spread garlic mayonnaise on inside top of rolls, add to top of sandwich. May slice in half to serve.